\par NL:\tab Rozin.
\par YM:\tab But he goes under the name, the }{\i\fs24 Rogachover}{\fs24  }{\i\fs24 Gaon}{\fs24 , }{\i\fs24 Rogachover}{\fs24 .  How you spell it, }{\i\fs24 Rogachover}{\fs24 
, the best way I can say it, Gaon [Brilliant Rabbi-teacher].  And he told the people, the board, when they came to him "Rebbe, we are in such-and-such a quandary, we don't have a }{\i\fs24 hazan}{\fs24 ," an so on, he said, "}{\i\fs24 
Yidden, oib yir vilt haben a Yid, a hazan, a Yid, nemt Hazan Mandel}{\fs24 ."}{\fs24\super 6{\footnote \pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\sa240\widctlpar
\tx-360\tx0\tx720\tx792\tx1440\tx1584\tx2160\tx2376\tx2880\tx3168\tx3600\tx3960\tx4140\tx4320\tx4578\tx4752\tx5040\tx5544\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {6}{\fs24 \tab 
\tab \tab \tab \tab \tab   }{Jews, if you want to have a Jew, a cantor, a Jew, take Cantor Mandel.}}}{\fs24 
\par NL:\tab Ah, you had }{\i\fs24 so}{\fs24  many offers!
\par YM:\tab Yes.  Yes.
\par NL:\tab Incredible.
\par YM:\tab So...
\par NL:\tab Did you pick up any impressions of Jewish life...
